data.description:
Welcome to Cliffs at Dover! Located in a desirable community, this immaculate 2-story townhome offers plenty of space and comfort. The lower level features a bedroom, ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet. You'll also find the laundry pantry and attached 2-car garage. Upstairs, the main level features an open concept floor plan, spacious living room, kitchen, second bedroom and full bathroom. The kitchen is fully equipped with modern appliances and plenty of counter space perfect for preparing meals and entertaining.

Additionally, the neighborhood offers plenty of amenities, including a community pool, gated security, and ample visitor parking. This is a great opportunity to own a beautiful home in a desirable community just minutes from Nellis Air Force Base, freeway access, schools, shopping and much more. Don't miss out on this chance to make this townhome your own!
